cc:Work.dc:title: Dynamixel Shield
cc:Work.dc:description: Support dynamixel protocol 1.0/2.0 Up to 16 DYNAMIXEL's can be controlled (Typically, each motor(XL-320 or XL430-W250) consumes 0.4 ~ 0.6A of current) Support SynWrite function Support RC-100 library Serial communication using software serial library DYNAMIXEL Shield library(v0.1.0 or above) requires DYNAMIXEL2Arduino library
